wiki.summary: Jimin of BTS released solo album on March 24, 2023, through Big Hit Music, it is primarily a pop, hip hop, and R&B record, with Pdogg, Ghstloop, and Evan responsible for production Jimin released studio album FACE. Comprising five songs, all co-written by Jimin, and one instrumental, the album was heavily inspired by the emotional impact of the COVID-19 pandemic on Jimin as a person and performer and addresses "themes of loneliness, wrestling with oneself, and finding freedom". wiki.content: Jimin of BTS released solo album on March 24, 2023, through Big Hit Music, it is primarily a pop, hip hop, and R&B record, with Pdogg, Ghstloop, and Evan responsible for production Jimin released studio album FACE. Comprising five songs, all co-written by Jimin, and one instrumental, the album was heavily inspired by the emotional impact of the COVID-19 pandemic on Jimin as a person and performer and addresses "themes of loneliness, wrestling with oneself, and finding freedom". Two singles were released in support of Face: the lead single Track page: Set Me Free Pt. 2 and the US Billboard Hot 100 number-one single "Like Crazy”. https://www.last.fm/music/Jimin/_/Set+Me+Free,+Pt.+2 Read more on Last.fm.
